Roll Will+d4 after resting for at least six hours to determine how much power you have that day.
When reading a scroll, test DR12 Prescence. If you succeed,
the scroll is activated and you reduce your total power accordingly.
Rolling below the DR causes you to lose d2 HP, and not be able to cast for 1h.
While rolling a Fumble causes the scroll to crumble to ashes, you lose d4 additional HP,
cannot cast for d6 days, and must roll on the Arcane Catastrophes table.
